```

The error at line 100 occurs because `output[output.findIndex(el => el.title === baseClass.title)]` returns `undefined` when the `findIndex` returns `-1` (i.e., when no item matches). This means `baseClass.title` doesn't match any item title in `output`, causing it to try to set `.subroutes` on `undefined`.

